        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1473939905" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2239728989829451336">This book is so real. It&apos;s almost too deep for a children&apos;s book. Even though it&apos;s about talking animals and Ivan&apos;s complexity of thought could be a little misleading, this book touches on so many great themes both superficial toward children, but also in general about humanity, if you&apos;re mature enough to understand it. This book was cute, sad, and something very new to me. I adored it and it is such a fast read that I highly recommend it!</span>
  <span id="freeText2239728989829451336" style="display:none">This book is so real. It's almost too deep for a children's book. Even though it's about talking animals and Ivan's complexity of thought could be a little misleading, this book touches on so many great themes both superficial toward children, but also in general about humanity, if you're mature enough to understand it. This book was cute, sad, and something very new to me. I adored it and it is such a fast read that I highly recommend it!</span>
