<span id="freeTextContainer5571197377862126299"><blockquote><i>I like colorful tales with black beginnings and stormy middles and cloudless blue-sky endings. But any story will do.</i> ~The One and Only Ivan<br/></blockquote><br/>::sniff:: What&apos;s that in my eye, this watery, salty substance? Crying? No. I&apos;m not crying. I&apos;m too old and cynical to cry. My tear ducts have long dried up. Really.<br/><br/>::sniff::<br/><br/>Oh for godsake, will someone hand me a tissue!<br/><br/>This is a sweet, adorable story that will tug at your heart-strings in the most uplifting way. It is a beautiful, tender tale of friendship, </span>
  <span id="freeText5571197377862126299" style="display:none"><blockquote><i>I like colorful tales with black beginnings and stormy middles and cloudless blue-sky endings. But any story will do.</i> ~The One and Only Ivan<br /></blockquote><br />::sniff:: What's that in my eye, this watery, salty substance? Crying? No. I'm not crying. I'm too old and cynical to cry. My tear ducts have long dried up. Really.<br /><br />::sniff::<br /><br />Oh for godsake, will someone hand me a tissue!<br /><br />This is a sweet, adorable story that will tug at your heart-strings in the most uplifting way. It is a beautiful, tender tale of friendship, acceptance and hope. The perfect antidote for the overworked, stressed out grinch in all of us. Read it!</span>
