        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2585912594" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer137275897402019251">This is a great book about wild animals being forced to live in bad conditions by ignorant humans. Ivan is based on a real Gorilla, and the fictional story Applegate wove pulled a bit on my heartstrings. I love Stella. It&apos;s a very, very sweet story. I can definitely see why people love this one so much! <br/><br/>I borrowed the audiobook from my library using an app, but then I found out there was illustrastions and felt like I was missing out. There are some prime examples if you google for them though, </span>
  <span id="freeText137275897402019251" style="display:none">This is a great book about wild animals being forced to live in bad conditions by ignorant humans. Ivan is based on a real Gorilla, and the fictional story Applegate wove pulled a bit on my heartstrings. I love Stella. It's a very, very sweet story. I can definitely see why people love this one so much! <br /><br />I borrowed the audiobook from my library using an app, but then I found out there was illustrastions and felt like I was missing out. There are some prime examples if you google for them though, so I got to see some of them. </span>
